      "title": "The tragedy of this pandemic is worsened if we fail to learn the...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=_hGxJau0kB0AX-KsA6Z\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ad4eeb7cc360b40f4ed85dfea18c1c9f\u0026oe=5FC6BDFC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3701589223207873/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe tragedy of this pandemic is worsened if we fail to learn the lessons COVID has taught us about a bloated and harmful carceral system that needlessly incarcerates thousands of Coloradans. We must act now to keep jail populations low and families together. Read the report:  \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/371MTZt\"\u003ehttps://bit.ly/371MTZt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3701589223207873/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/123359791_3701589226541206_9134239334579411813_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=rhFomlharRMAX_xKheq\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=6\u0026oh=30f92395b8539c6eee786b2b7e4875b4\u0026oe=5FC5AC2A\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says '46% DROP in jail population 20,000+ MORE people living free EVERY MONTH 6,000 FEWER people in jail EVERY DAY $210 MILLION SAVED if jail populations stayed low ACLU co The time to act and build a better Colorado is now.'\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says '46% DROP in jail population 20,000+ MORE people living free EVERY MONTH 6,000 FEWER people in jail EVERY DAY $210 MILLION SAVED if jail populations stayed low ACLU co The time to act and build a better Colorado is now.'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e",
