      "title": "We must take action to bring our neighbors safely home or more...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=_hGxJau0kB0AX-KsA6Z\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ad4eeb7cc360b40f4ed85dfea18c1c9f\u0026oe=5FC6BDFC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/posts/3696387693728026\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe must take action to bring our neighbors safely home or more people will die behind bars and in the community. Safe decarceration should be part of \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jaredpolis/\"\u003eGovernor Jared Polis\u003c/a\u003e's plan to protect public health. It's necessary and possible, here's how: \u003ca href=\"https://acluco-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/aclu_decarcerationreport_100720_final.pdf\"\u003ehttps://acluco-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/…/aclu_decarceration…\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.denverpost.com/2020/10/29/colorado-prison-inmate-dies-coronavirus/\"\u003ehttps://www.denverpost.com/…/colorado-prison-inmate-dies-c…/\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.denverpost.com/2020/10/29/colorado-prison-inmate-dies-coronavirus/\"\u003eFour men incarcerated in Colorado’s prisons have died after contracting COVID-19.\u003cimg src=\"https://external.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDNcH7Z1UPP2f0f\u0026w=540\u0026h=282\u0026url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.denverpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Frenewable_ac12785.jpg%3Fw%3D1024%26h%3D681\u0026cfs=1\u0026upscale=1\u0026fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher\u0026_nc_cb=1\u0026_nc_hash=AQAvxOnaYaQ-LY7Y\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"262\" caption=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003edenverpost.com\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA fourth Colorado inmate has died after experiencing COVID-19 symptoms\u003c/p\u003eFour men incarcerated in Colorado’s prisons have died after contracting COVID-19.\u003ca href=\"https://www.denverpost.com/2020/10/29/colorado-prison-inmate-dies-coronavirus/\"\u003eFour men incarcerated in Colorado’s prisons have died after contracting COVID-19.\u003c/a\u003e",
