      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=_hGxJau0kB0AX-KsA6Z\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ad4eeb7cc360b40f4ed85dfea18c1c9f\u0026oe=5FC6BDFC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3693115890721873/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eOver two million Americans spend each night behind bars. Mass incarceration is an unbearable burden that traumatizes incarcerated people, families and communities. In the face of a global pandemic, thousands of Coloradans have been released. Now we must act to keep our neighbors home. Read our report: \u003ca href=\"https://aclu-co.org/campaigns/covid-19-decarceration/\"\u003ehttps://aclu-co.org/campaigns/covid-19-decarceration/\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3693115890721873/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/123101288_3693115894055206_5695465159785602421_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=bR91NDOc-sEAX8hNL3v\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=6\u0026oh=27f2e19bdcd5d846d4baa989d11099f8\u0026oe=5FC65270\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says 'IN THREE MONTHS, jail populations dropped to levels not seen in thirty years. There was also a 4% drop in crime. Colorado does NOT have to choose between public safety and public health. ACLU co'\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says 'IN THREE MONTHS, jail populations dropped to levels not seen in thirty years. There was also a 4% drop in crime. Colorado does NOT have to choose between public safety and public health. ACLU co'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e",
