      "title": "If you are notified that your ballot was rejected due to a...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=_hGxJau0kB0AX-KsA6Z\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ad4eeb7cc360b40f4ed85dfea18c1c9f\u0026oe=5FC6BDFC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3690287577671371/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you are notified that your ballot was rejected due to a discrepancy in your signature, you can now easily fix it over text. Secretary of State, Jena Griswold, announced that Colorado will offer a new TXT2Cure program. Just text \"Colorado\" to 2VOTE (28683), and you will receive instructions on how to cure your ballot.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e For more info, read this article from the Secretary of State: \u003cbr /\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.sos.state.co.us/pubs/newsRoom/pressReleases/2020/PR20201007TXT2Cure.html\"\u003ehttps://www.sos.state.co.us/…/…/2020/PR20201007TXT2Cure.html\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3690287577671371/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s526x296/122993431_3690287581004704_432827143675985832_o.png?_nc_cat=107\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=Fxe2vXPrKQ4AX8VcDeb\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026oh=ad914317e80eb1d9f27c88635cc1b860\u0026oe=5FC4B3D6\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says 'ReturnEnvelope Rejected Ballot? If you're notified of signature discrepancy, text \"Colorado' to 2VOTE (28683), click on the link, and follow the steps provided. For more information, visit the Secretary of State's website at www.sos.state.co.us. Fix it with TXT2Cure ACLU Colorado'\" width=\"500\" height=\"262\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says 'ReturnEnvelope Rejected Ballot? If you're notified of signature discrepancy, text \"Colorado' to 2VOTE (28683), click on the link, and follow the steps provided. For more information, visit the Secretary of State's website at www.sos.state.co.us. Fix it with TXT2Cure ACLU Colorado'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/votinginformationcenter/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v3/yw/r/uboafmf-0hy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" /\u003eVisit the Voting Information Center for official election resources and local updates. Get Voting Information\u003c/a\u003e",
      "date_published": "2020-10-27T08:53:02-06:00",
      "date_modified": "2020-10-27T08:53:02-06:00",
