      "url": "https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3688485921184870/",
      "title": "If you're visiting a polling place in person this election,...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=_hGxJau0kB0AX-KsA6Z\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ad4eeb7cc360b40f4ed85dfea18c1c9f\u0026oe=5FC6BDFC\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3688485921184870/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you're visiting a polling place in person this election, please remember that clothing and accessories with political messages on them are not allowed. This includes pins, t-shirts, hats, or other apparel that display a candidate or any issue on the ballot. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e You have the right to vote free of intimidation or coercion. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e More info and rules about voting in this year's election: \u003ca href=\"https://www.sos.state.co.us/pubs/elections/FAQs/crimesRulesFAQ.html\"\u003ehttps://www.sos.state.co.us/…/elec…/FAQs/crimesRulesFAQ.html\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/3688485921184870/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/s526x296/123046296_3688485924518203_3545059350820364962_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=1G1MzDq73jQAX9m8oB1\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=7\u0026oh=eb0a7425abd4ecbdb6708c7884074ee0\u0026oe=5FC47887\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says 'ACLU CO What not to wear within 100 feet of a polling center: MAKE AGAIN (Any apparel explicitly displaying any candidate.)'\" width=\"500\" height=\"262\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says 'ACLU CO What not to wear within 100 feet of a polling center: MAKE AGAIN (Any apparel explicitly displaying any candidate.)'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/votinginformationcenter/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v3/yw/r/uboafmf-0hy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" /\u003eVisit the Voting Information Center for official election resources and local updates. Get Voting Information\u003c/a\u003e",
